{"id":53656,"date":"2024-02-08T19:33:01","date_gmt":"2024-02-08T14:03:01","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=53656"},"modified":"2024-02-08T19:33:05","modified_gmt":"2024-02-08T14:03:05","slug":"brick-wall-design-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/brick-wall-design-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"Brick Wall Bedroom Designs for an Instant Upgrade"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Make a statement and add character to your home with brick wall designs for your bedroom space; here&#8217;s how!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Don&#8217;t let Pinterest and Instagram trap you into neutral, muted, dull, monochrome homes lacking character. There is plenty you can do with your homes, and it shouldn&#8217;t limit you from experimenting with rustic, industrial styles that aren&#8217;t confined to the trends that follow on social media\u2014cue in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/brick-wall-designs\/\">brick wall designs<\/a> that offer an instant makeover to your space without much hassle.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>These wall styles have forever been part of the interior design ecosystem and are much loved by fans of rustic charm and industrial designs. Here&#8217;s how to make the most of this bare brick wall design for your bedroom interiors.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Brick Wall Design As A Wall Accent<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Understandably, brick wall designs can be a little too much when incorporated across the length and breadth of your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/bedroom-design\/\">bedroom design<\/a>; however, just a sliver of it can amplify the character of your home. As shown in the image, this style doesn&#8217;t take anything away from your peaceful sanctuary while also making a statement. It is not distracting and adds a more chic vibe to the space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/08192711\/contemporary-bedroom-with-brick-wall-design.jpg\" alt=\"Contemporary bedroom features a half-brick wall design with a grey-coloured wall\" class=\"wp-image-53660\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/08192711\/contemporary-bedroom-with-brick-wall-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/08192711\/contemporary-bedroom-with-brick-wall-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/08192711\/contemporary-bedroom-with-brick-wall-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/08192711\/contemporary-bedroom-with-brick-wall-design-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/08192711\/contemporary-bedroom-with-brick-wall-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A peaceful contemporary bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Bedroom Foam Bricks Design in Green<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If bare brick wall designs are too in-your-face for your home, this style is a great choice. It is subtle, modern in approach, and aligns with the interior design trends of the season. This gorgeous bedroom design has all the elements infusing modern industrial charm into your home. The monochromatic wall art frames, solid grey upholstered bench, a sturdy bed, and a simple rug complete the look. What more do you need?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/08192643\/bedroom-foam-bricks-design-in-green.jpg\" alt=\"Bedroom foam bricks are designed in green, adding a touch of colour and texture to the room's decor\" class=\"wp-image-53657\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/u